byline.original: By DECLAN WALSH and AMINA ISMAIL

abstract: Egyptian police are treating firebomb attack on Cairo nightclub which killed 16 people as crime, not terrorism.
lead_paragraph: While the capital has been struck by several militant attacks this year, the police said they were not treating the El Sayad club bombing as an act of terrorism.

headline.main: Firebomb Attack on Cairo Nightclub Kills at Least 16
